      "Implemented user-centered designs and interfaces",
      "Integrated Google Maps and navigation features",
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "Founder & Software Engineer",
    company: "ERASOFT",
    period: "July 2024 - Current",
    highlights: [
      "Founded ERASOFT, leading development of two parallel MVP projects",
      "Created WebRTC-based digital counter application using Flutter and Firebase",
      "Pioneered real-time translation in video calls using WebRTC and OpenAI",
